  - identify_combination(cards): Identifies and validates the Dou Dizhu combination represented by a list of cards.
  - can_beat(new_comb, prev_comb): Determines if a new combination can beat the previous one under Dou Dizhu rules.
  - Helper functions for detecting straights, pair-straights, triple-sequences, triple-with-wings, four-with-attachments, and more.

